What you need to know:

The CS had allowed management of universities to decide on their respective dates to ask students to report to campuses based on their individual assessments.Next week, Interior Cabinet Secretary Fred Matiang’i and his Health counterpart Mutahi Kagwe will co-chair the national consultative conference to chart the country’s post Covid-19 future.A source who attended the meeting told the Nation that the CS had allowed management of universities to decide on their respective dates to ask students to report to campuses based on their individual assessments.